data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious Westward Pointe subdivision! This stunning 2940 square foot residence, meticulously crafted by KB Homes in 2015, offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and timeless elegance.    As you step through the front door, you are greeted by an abundance of natural light, accentuating the spacious open floor plan. With 5 bedrooms and 3 1/2 bathrooms, including a convenient half bathroom downstairs, this home is designed to accommodate both family living and entertaining with ease.    The heart of the home is the kitchen, featuring ample cabinet space. The adjacent dining area seamlessly flows into the inviting living room, creating a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings and celebrations.    One of the distinctive features of this home is the owner's suite located on the first floor, providing privacy and convenience. The en-suite bathroom is a luxurious retreat, complete with a walk-in closet, shower, and a double vanity.    Recent upgrades enhance the home's aesthetic appeal and functionality, including fresh paint throughout, as well as new tile flooring and plush carpeting. These thoughtful enhancements elevate the overall ambiance and showcase the home's commitment to quality craftsmanship.    With its prime location in the sought-after Westward Pointe subdivision, this home provides easy access to local amenities, schools, and parks. Immerse yourself in the vibrant community and take advantage of everything this thriving neighborhood has to offer.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own - schedule a showing today and envision the lifestyle that awaits you in this meticulously cared-for home!
